comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) moves alongside Gobert (UTA) and marginal contact occurs as Gobert mishandles the ball in the lane.
Wagner (ORL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Gobert (UTA) in the lane.
Hampton (ORL) rests his hand on Bogdanovic's (UTA) left hip as he elevates for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Bogdanovic's back as Hampton secures the ball.
O'Neale (UTA) moves forward toward Anthony (ORL) and incidental contact occurs with Anthony's front after he mishandles the ball.
Hampton (ORL) goes to, not through, Gobert's (UTA) space when contact occurs as he attempts to go over the pick.
Gobert (UTA) firms up in his screening position in Hampton's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Hampton (ORL) is moving forward toward Mitchell (UTA) and incidental body contact occurs after Mitchell dribbles the ball off of his foot.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball last touches Mitchell's (UTA) foot before going out of bounds.
Anthony (ORL) brings his off-arm toward Bogdanovic's (UTA) front and marginal contact occurs as Anthony releases away at the end of the drive.
Anthony (ORL) maintains his left foot as his pivot after picking up his dribble in the lane.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Hampton's (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is moving somewhat laterally when marginal body contact occurs with Mitchell (UTA) after Mitchell's gather.

O'Neale (UTA) swipes forward and makes fingertip contact with the ball before incidental contact occurs with Anthony's (ORL) front. O'Neale then moves forward and marginal contact occurs with Anthony's side as the ball remains loose.
Anthony (ORL) legally gathers the ball and re-starts his dribble after the ball is dislodged.
O'Neale (UTA) swipes forward and makes clean contact with the ball as Anthony (ORL) crosses over. Any contact to Anthony's front/arm after the ball becomes loose is deemed incidental.
Anthony (ORL) and Gobert (UTA) make incidental body contact with one another as they each dive to the floor in pursuit of the loose ball.
Bogdanovic (UTA) makes contact with the ball and the part of Harris' (ORL) hand that is on the ball, and dislodges it away before he and O'Neale (UTA) make incidental arm contact with Harris.
Harris (ORL) and Bogdanovic (UTA) make incidental body contact with one another after the ball becomes loose.
Mitchell (UTA) brushes Hampton's (ORL) front after the release of his jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs during the follow-through.

Harris (ORL) drives through Gobert (UTA) and dislodges him from his screening position during the inbound and a defensive foul should be called. The initial contact from Harris causes the ensuing contact from Gobert.
Ingles (UTA) commits a take foul on Anthony (ORL).
